raw_text: The bathroom is located on the east side, in between the kitchen and the master room. It is also east of the living room. The kitchen is also connected on its lower east corner, the bathroom is on the east side, and the master on its north-east corner. The room has eight sides, but has an area of about 22ft x 10ft.
